<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC2">
<l>nāviṉāl naviṟṟu iṉpam eytiṉēṉ</l>
<l>mēviṉēṉ avaṉ poṇṇaṭi meymmaiyē</l>
<l>tēvu maṟṟu aṟiyēṉ kurukūr nampi</l>
<l>pāviṉ iṉṉicai pāṭit tirivaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having said [his name] with [my] tongue, I obtained pleasure.</l>
<l>I learned the reality of his golden feet.</l>
<l>I do not know another God.</l>
<l>I wander, singing the sweet songs of the Kurukūr Lord’s poems.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
